{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Spheres Are the Key </strong></h2>Use the spheres power to light the torches and complete the level. But it won't always be easy: you'll need to aim your throws well and launch them before the time limit runs out...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/02_Sphere_Target.gif?t=1737496295\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Two Campaigns, Two stories</strong></h2>Uncover Enid's story as you recover the forgotten fragments, or team up with a friend to unravel all the secrets of the two-player campaign. Each campaign has its own levels!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090//extras/Coop.gif?t=1737496295\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Over 120 Levels to Conquer</strong></h2>Each campaign features 4 worlds to explore, with over 60 levels each. But the challenge doesn't end there, as you can replay each level to improve your time and become the best!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/Worlds.gif?t=1737496295\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Epic Boss Fights!</strong></h2>At the end of each world, you'll face a powerful boss, each with their own unique mechanics. Get ready to apply everything you've learned during your adventure to emerge victorious in these battles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492090/extras/Boss.gif?t=1737496295\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Find the hidden collectibles and the secret levels!</strong></h2>Find the hidden collectibles in some levels to unlock skins and customize your characters. Make sure to explore every corner: to play the secret levels, you'll need to light special torches...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=